channel.title: Posted My Server, Error?
channel.description:
Tried registering my server on the SSP, I logged in with the username and password it gives you. Except it's been around 3 hours since I posted it, And it should only take around 30 minutes? I tried to use the Moparscape client and connect, But I get this error on my VPS server
Invalid Client Version: 317
So does this mean I wont get my server verified anytime soon? Or...
Thanks in advance to whoever can help me out!
